title: #92Noon! Flash/Miller/Tucker/Micheletti/Farmer
description: Cordarrelle Patterson joins for a catch-up in the second segment, and Lions vox Dan Miller offers thoughts on the Stafford/Goff trade to end the first hour...Trent Tucker in the mix on hoops for a couple segments midway thru...Pat Micheletti on hockey, and LA Times writer Sam Farmer closes the show!
